---
title: Kids' Mini Hummus Pinwheels Serves 2 | with Feta and Cucumbers
description: These Mediterranean-inspired hummus bites are the perfect way to sneak some extra veg and flavour into your kiddo's lunch. A crisp gala apple alongside adds some natural sweetness!
